Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认郁金香有重力波反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蜻蜓级大小以上的战舰来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要的时候就用唐菖蒲撞它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波又增强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:42.36,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)\bord0\shad0\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(340,380)\fscy150\fs59}变温的『冷酷方程式』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在本舰已回到通常空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标正在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来后立刻就回到自己岗位进入非常警戒体制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  舰长  舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回到通常空间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  你为什么会在那里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看外面的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将情况投影到展望室的银幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在位于月球附近  在蜥蜴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波炮广域放射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后张开力场后退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些混帐在搞什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没死人  听好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们再继续攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也会赌上第二舰队的名誉迎击！以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了这是误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说句误会就没事的话战争可就轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球方面的损害如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸中的万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来伤患不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也难怪他们会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看清楚就攻击他们是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是我们被军人救的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你待在舰桥上的话  应该看得清状况的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人你知道发生什么事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道好想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急情况时待在展望室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不谨慎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  伊妮斯小姐当时也在  应该没有出轨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出轨?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候  那个喜欢说明的要能出现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.53,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯睡眠中！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.55,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  够了  吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河在哪里做了什么又不关我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信天河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信天河?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是待命中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河天河天河天河…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自散开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战术呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视情况而定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰继续维持力场行进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了给重力波炮充电
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么会在那里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该在舰桥上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  反正也是跟明人在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  我有话跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总公司有事找你商量…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说总公司有事跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？ 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十架才打中三架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来蚱蜢的力场好像也强化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会进化的机器?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近战可是我的专长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  天河怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河  快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  白痴  快点报告战况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人君  喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河  撑着点  我马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河机完全被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…手不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.00,2:42:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去救援…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说  已经去救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会害怕才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部给我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方消灭了两成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波测知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多连装的重力波炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  是什么  这个模组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新型的啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动机也很小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连肌肤也滑溜溜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就搞一辈子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这新型是什么时候造出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说我们的小AESTI是最新式的  真是太诈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你们消失在火星八个月这期间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球方面也有了新的生力军这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赤月流行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大波斯菊来的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧  舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望你能够接受这个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否别  抚子将遭到唐昌蒲旗下的联合宇宙军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和木星蜥蜴的夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还得和大家商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先把抚子收容至大波斯菊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大波斯菊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的二号舰  大波斯菊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱导光束确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲出郁金香时瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过至少在火星的战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球时间过了八个月是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附带一提这期间NERGAL和联合军和解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造了新战舰夺回月球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的看法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个待会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  NERGAL总公司与联合军共同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此抚子也随之被编入地球联合海军极东方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们要成为军人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暂时性支援而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁呐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月流行  是来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我就像聚集在自由之旗下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂泊宇宙的海贼这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过像你这样的美人真是一点也不适合粗鲁的军队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要放弃火星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次你有把握赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打不赢也要打到赢为止这种话一点价值也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本公司也负担不起这样的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从战略角度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和联合军合作或许很妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们当职业军人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的话退出不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领了薪水后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位就是将成为你们朋友的亚唐银二君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫亚唐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  我更帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  地球的人跟我们一样是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该怎么说  真是大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为门是开着的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们跑不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克兹这家伙  这么急着抢功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人出动!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健他们是激钢人的驾驶员?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好笑的话就不要看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然不会了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然喜欢这种动画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那更应该乐意抚子加入军方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己又怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是单纯的喜欢战争罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有感觉到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于印象回馈系统的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗本能如火上浇油一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因为战争就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是讨厌为了战争而战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能有除了战斗外的生存价值或工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就明说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  激钢剑  飞天之势！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是用运动决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提因为重力几乎接近零所以要小…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说小心也来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像动画那样爽快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河君  利用反作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶  可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错嘛  天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是实战的话  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS队准备迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  明人  就差你了  快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太深入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你期待的实战喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采凤仙阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  实在是很安全  真是好战法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是因为喜欢战斗才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此为什么要登上抚子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上不上关你什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生畜生畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快放开蚱蜢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样他听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河机  进入月球阴影了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河机请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波束切断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河机请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇难了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇难?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道没办法靠自力回航吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自抚子的重力波束中断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是只能靠备用电池飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多飞五分钟就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇难的时候最好在原地等候救援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若从这里稍微接近点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生还的可能性就比较大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  抚子正在修理中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这种状态出动的话正是绝佳目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大波斯菊有一般的战斗机吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.30,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大波斯菊  重力弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料只有四小时的份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有危险就立刻回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真没想到你会去接他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为你是比较聪明的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是现代的舰长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是没受过战斗训练吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入养成所前就已经取得飞行员资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  阿纯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹射器一号  打开闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源还可以撑八小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在这之前氧气会先用光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西居然会成为提示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像激钢人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人果然是我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会害怕了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到必须救你们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何心里就不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是为了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那种事了  氧气只剩三十分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有三个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以目前的加速度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到达抚子能锁定的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要两个小时以上…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个小时以后我们三个早结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样张开紧急用太阳帆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以提高加速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也要四十分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最下面的数字呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样在二十分钟内…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只有一个人的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十分钟是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说只要有人下去就可以早点回到抚子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样补充能量后马上回来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人是驾驶员  所以必须留下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我决定吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那百合香好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃? 是因为我比较重?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  对我来说太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实最近我的食欲不错变得比较重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  三人一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护什么而舍弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是跟军方一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠毅力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想呼唤着明日…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.07,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有能源了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是走错方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是加速不够吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人一直都是在危机时解救我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对百合香来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底不过是崇拜的偶像罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心喜欢明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  对我来说明人也是非常重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道跟惠的意思是不是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在展望室?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  你吻过小惠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯恢复了也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会说要去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很无聊嘛  他不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月  我要留在抚子上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心里有东西沸腾着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有要守护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是凯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是为了地球而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但绝不是因为他想打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说  我也想探寻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷  就是这样就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才像他的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就结束了  真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这位是从今天起派到我们舰上来的新提督
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉娜金城王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被重新任命为副操舵士值勤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会长秘书也要来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你也会在舰上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从火星进行玻色子跳耀那瞬间的天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向目标海域!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.36,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}万能战舰最大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到谜样的命令的抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰封的海域看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:53.30,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}白魔来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而明人能安全归来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.10,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}战斗与恋爱与理性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面有不得了的事件在明人前面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  机动战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:01.84,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}惠会赢还是百合香会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹的作战『接吻吗?』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到惠姐姐穿水手服喔
